rows.label: qst10205_msg001
rows.name: The Nopopo Daikon is ready, mo! (Temp)

rows.label: qst10205_msg0002
rows.name:
The seeds my grandma left me,
saying she wanted to make
something even more delicious...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0003
rows.name:
they've finally borne fruit in Umama's
field with your fertilizer, mo!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0004
rows.name:
This vegetable... I'll name
it Nopopo Daikon, mo!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0005
rows.name:
I said I'd let you be the first to
eat it when it was ready, but...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0006
rows.name:
I couldn't wait and took a bite, mo! It's
packed with flavor, full of energy! It tastes
like it'll make you live a long time, mo!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0007
rows.name:
I feel like I saw my
grandma's happy face, mo...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0008
rows.name:
This wouldn't have been
possible without your help,
mo! I'm so grateful, mo.

rows.label: qst10205_msg0009
rows.name:
Mo... I haven't sold any vegetables
yet, so I don't have any money...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0010
rows.name:
All I can do is give you some Nopopo
Daikon as a thank you, mo...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0011
rows.name: Is that okay, mo? Oh! That's right, mo!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0012
rows.name:
If you help me again, I'll
give you lots of the Nopopo
Daikon that's ready, mo!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0013
rows.name:
If you ever want Nopopo
Daikon, just let me know, mo.
